It would be cool to have the MapTraQ part from ScanSat, the default part for scansat is really ugly and massive compared to the CubeSat. Can we have this pleeeeaaassseee? *puppy eyes*

Here is a modulemanager config that adds MapTraq to the tape antennas. I'm not sure if this will be a permanent addition to the mod but it'll get you started. As far as a MapTraq part we may make some antennas in the future that are better suited to officially include MapTraq functionality. 

@PART[Antenna_Tape1]
{
    MODULE
    {
        name = SCANsat
        sensorType = 0
        fov = 0
        min_alt = 0
        max_alt = 0
        best_alt = 0
        power = 0.05
        scanName = Eyeball Scan
    }
}
@PART[Antenna_Tape2]
{
    MODULE
    {
        name = SCANsat
        sensorType = 0
        fov = 0
        min_alt = 0
        max_alt = 0
        best_alt = 0
        power = 0.05
        scanName = Eyeball Scan
    }
}

That box was a hand-painted object in Photoshop for the purposes of the forum banner. However, it has been noted that the community wants that made into a part. While it was funny that people wanted to "play with the box it came in", we haven't committed to making that a real part quite yet. We still have another few alpha releases we want to do to get V.1 out, so after that we'll have some time to make some extra gag-parts.
